snippet.title: LISA - DREAM feat. Kentaro Sakaguchi (Official Short Film MV)
snippet.description:
LISA’s debut album, ‘Alter Ego’ is out now. Listen here: https://lisa.lnk.to/AlterEgo   
Shop vinyl, CDs, photobooks and more: https://lnk.to/LisaStore 

Follow LISA: 
http://www.instagram.com/lalalalisa_m
https://www.tiktok.com/@lalalalisa_m
https://www.youtube.com/@lalalalisa_m

Follow WeAreLLOUD:
http://www.instagram.com/wearelloud
https://www.tiktok.com/@wearelloud
http://www.facebook.com/wearelloud
https://www.youtube.com/@wearelloud/videos

Lyrics:
I’ve been thinking 
That I got no idea what you’re thinking 
Are you happy? Are you sad?
Are you always gonna hate me for that night in Tokyo? 
When it ended 
I kinda hoped that it’d be open ended
But you never looked back 
Well I guess you can’t hold on to something once you let it go 
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I guess that I’m taking what I can get 
‘Cause I don’t get nothing new from your friends 
If you got the harder side of the break 
Then why is it harder for me to take 
There’s so much I might never get to say, ay
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I-I-I know it’s only in my mind
Playing three nights on the stereo
Like a movie scene, DiCaprio 
Oh l-I-I put my make up on just to fall asleep
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is something we’ll never be
It’s bittersweet
Can we be friends at least

My baby

🐍  Anaconda 

Over the past few months, whispers have been growing louder about a potential reboot of the cult classic creature feature Anaconda. The latest buzz? Hollywood heavyweight Dwayne “The Rock” Johnson may be circling the lead role in a big-budget reimagining of the 1997 jungle horror-thriller.

According to multiple industry insiders, the project is said to be in “active discussions” at Sony’s Columbia Pictures, with early development materials reportedly blending survival-horror with the kind of large-scale action sequences that have become Johnson’s trademark.

The original Anaconda, starring Jennifer Lopez, Ice Cube, and Jon Voight, followed a documentary crew’s perilous encounter with a massive snake deep in the Amazon rainforest. The film became a surprise box office hit, earning over $135 million worldwide and spawning several sequels.

snippet.title: " LIHIM, LUPA AT LABAN !! "  AUG. 11, 2025 | FPJ's Batang Quiapo ADVANCE Trailer Episode645
snippet.description:
Sa gitna ng lumalagablab na digmaan ng pamilya, kapangyarihan, at katotohanan, tumindig ang mga bayani ng karaniwang tao. Si Marites, isang anak na handang ialay ang lahat para sa pamilya. Si Tindeng at Alfredo, simbolo ng tibay ng puso sa kabila ng pagkakagapos. Si Tanggol, ang kandidatong hindi binili ng sistema—kundi pinanday ng prinsipyo.

Samantalang lumulubog sa sarili niyang galit at paghihiganti si Pilar, unti-unti namang nabubunyag ang mga madidilim na lihim ng pamilyang Guerrero—mga lihim na maaaring bumagsak sa buong lungsod.

Sa bawat putok ng baril, sa bawat sampal, sa bawat suntok—lumalantad ang mga tunay na kulay ng mga taong dati’y may maskara. At sa likod ng ingay ng karahasan, naririnig ang bulong ng pag-asa: na sa gitna ng dilim, may mga pusong patuloy na lumalaban para sa tama.

ito ay isang teleseryeng puno ng paninindigan, rebelasyon, at pagmamahal, na magpapaalala sa atin:
Ang kapangyarihan ay lilipas, ngunit ang katotohanan ay mananatili.

snippet.title: One Punch Man Season 3 - Official Trailer (English Subtitles)
snippet.description:
"One-Punch Man” returns with Season 3! Check out the latest trailer for the continuation of this series!

Saitama is a hero who only became a hero for fun. After three years of “special training,” he’s become so strong that he’s practically invincible. In fact, he’s too strong—even his mightiest opponents are taken out with a single punch. Alongside Genos, his faithful disciple, Saitama performs his official hero duties as a member of the Hero Association. One day, monsters claiming to be from the Monster Association suddenly appeared, taking a child of Hero Association executive hostage. The S-class heroes gather and plan a raid on the Monster Association hideout to rescue the hostage. Meanwhile, Garou, a “human monster” who was taken by the Monster Association during a battle with the heroes, awakens in the Monster Association hideout."
